#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:4
msgid "三维物件"
msgstr "3D Items"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:6
msgid "在 :ref:`3d_scene` 这一节中我们介绍了三维空间中的一些基础概念和知识，我们知道了在三维空间中，一般来说需要："
msgstr ""
"In the :ref:`3d_scene` section, we introduced some basic concepts and knowledge about 3D space, and we learned that in 3D "
"space, one usually needs:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:8
msgid "合适的摄像机视角"
msgstr "An appropriate camera angle"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:10
msgid "让物件在 ``IN`` / ``OUT`` 方向上有所移动或是在三维空间中旋转"
msgstr "Make items move along the ``IN`` / ``OUT`` direction or rotate in 3D space"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:12
msgid "例如上一节中我们看到的例子："
msgstr "For example, the example we saw in the previous section:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:20
msgid "几何结构与曲面类型"
msgstr "Geometric Structures and Surface Types"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:22
msgid ""
"除了使用那些我们先前已经知道的平面几何物件让他们在三维空间中移动，JAnim 中还内置了若干的 **空间几何结构** 以及 **曲面类型"
"**"
msgstr ""
"In addition to using the planar geometric items we already know to move them in 3D space, JAnim also includes several "
"built-in **spatial geometric structures** and **surface types**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:24
msgid ""
"首先我们讨论 **空间几何结构** ，举例来说，比如球体 :class:`~.Sphere` 、圆环 :class:`~.Torus` 、 圆柱 :class:`~.Cylinder` "
"等， 他们定义了这些三维图形的几何信息"
msgstr ""
"First, let us discuss **spatial geometric structures**. For example, spheres :class:`~.Sphere`, tori :class:`~.Torus`, "
"cylinders :class:`~.Cylinder`, and so on define the geometric information of these 3D shapes"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:27
msgid ""
"但是，这些几何信息并不是能够直接显示在画面上的物件，我们还需要通过 :meth:`~.SurfaceGeometry.into` 将其转换为特定 **曲面类"
"型** 的物件，包括："
msgstr ""
"However, this geometric information is not directly displayable as items on screen; we still need to convert it into a "
"specific **surface type** of item through :meth:`~.SurfaceGeometry.into`, including:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:29
msgid "``.into('checker')`` 得到棋盘格样式的曲面"
msgstr "``.into('checker')`` produces a checkerboard-style surface"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:31
msgid "``.into('vchecker')`` 也是得到棋盘格样式的曲面，但是每个面都是单独的 :class:`~.VItem`"
msgstr "``.into('vchecker')`` also produces a checkerboard-style surface, but each face is a separate :class:`~.VItem`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:33
msgid "``.into('wire')`` 得到线框样式的曲面"
msgstr "``.into('wire')`` produces a wireframe-style surface"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:35
msgid "``.into('smooth')`` 得到平滑样式的曲面"
msgstr "``.into('smooth')`` produces a smooth-style surface"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:37
msgid "``.into('dots')`` 得到点集样式的曲面"
msgstr "``.into('dots')`` produces a point-cloud-style surface"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:41
msgid ""
"``'checker'`` 类型和 ``'vchecker'`` 类型的区别在于，前者是整体渲染的棋盘格表面，后者每个面都是单独的 :class:`~.VItem` ，各"
"有优劣：整体渲染性能更佳，而独立表面可以有更高的灵活度"
msgstr ""
"The difference between the ``'checker'`` and ``'vchecker'`` types is that the former renders a checkerboard surface as a "
"whole, while the latter renders each face as a separate :class:`~.VItem`. The former generally performs better, while the "
"latter offers greater flexibility."

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:43
msgid "比如这里演示了圆环的若干种 **曲面类型** 显示出来的样子："
msgstr "For example, this demonstrates several **surface types** for a torus:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:15
msgid ""
"shape = Torus(1, 0.5)\n"
"torus1 = shape.into('checker')\n"
"torus2 = shape.into('wire')\n"
"torus3 = shape.into('smooth')\n"
"torus4 = shape.into('dots')\n"
"\n"
"group = Group(torus1, torus2, torus3, torus4).show()\n"
"group.points.arrange_in_grid()\n"
"self.camera.points.set(orientation=quat(0.36, -0.04, -0.11, 0.93))\n"
"self.camera.points.shift([0, -0.3, -0.32])"
msgstr ""
"shape = Torus(1, 0.5)\n"
"torus1 = shape.into('checker')\n"
"torus2 = shape.into('wire')\n"
"torus3 = shape.into('smooth')\n"
"torus4 = shape.into('dots')\n"
"\n"
"group = Group(torus1, torus2, torus3, torus4).show()\n"
"group.points.arrange_in_grid()\n"
"self.camera.points.set(orientation=quat(0.36, -0.04, -0.11, 0.93))\n"
"self.camera.points.shift([0, -0.3, -0.32])"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:60
msgid "以及一个更完整的演示："
msgstr "And a more complete demonstration:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/3d_items.rst:20
msgid ""
"from janim.imports import *\n"
"\n"
"class _ThreeDShapesExampleSub(Timeline):\n"
"    def __init__(self, shape_type: str, background_color: JAnimColor):\n"
"        super().__init__()\n"
"        self.shape_type = shape_type\n"
"        self.background_color = background_color\n"
"\n"
"    def construct(self):\n"
"        if self.shape_type == 'smooth':\n"
"            axes = ThreeDAxes((-8, 8), (-8, 8), (-8, 8)).apply_depth_test()\n"
"            self.prepare(FadeIn(axes, at=1))\n"
"\n"
"        background = FrameRect(fill_alpha=1, fill_color=self.background_color, stroke_alpha=0, depth=100)\n"
"        background.fix_in_frame()\n"
"        self.prepare(FadeIn(background, at=1.5, duration=3))\n"
"\n"
"        for shape in [Torus(2, 1), Cylinder(2, 4), Cone(2, 4)]:\n"
"            item = shape.into(self.shape_type).show()\n"
"            self.play(self.RotatingCamera(), duration=4)\n"
"            item.hide()\n"
"        \n"
"    def RotatingCamera(self):\n"
"        return AnimGroup(\n"
"            DataUpdater(\n"
"                self.camera,\n"
"                lambda data, p: data.points.rotate(TAU * p.alpha, axis=RIGHT),\n"
"                rate_func=linear\n"
"            ),\n"
"            DataUpdater(\n"
"                self.camera,\n"
"                lambda data, p: data.points.rotate(TAU * p.alpha, axis=OUT),\n"
"                rate_func=linear\n"
"            ),\n"
"        )\n"
"\n"
"class ThreeDShapesExample(Timeline):\n"
"    def construct(self):\n"
"        subs = [\n"
"            _ThreeDShapesExampleSub(type, color).build().to_item()\n"
"            for type, color in zip(\n"
"                ['checker', 'wire', 'smooth', 'dots'],\n"
"                ['#000022', '#000033', '#000033', '#000022']\n"
"            )\n"
"        ]\n"
"        subs[0].show()\n"
"\n"
"        effects = [\n"
"            RectClip(sub, anchor=ORIGIN)\n"
"            for sub in subs\n"
"        ]\n"
"        effects[0].show().depth.set(-1)\n"
"        \n"
"        dirs = [UL, UR, DL, DR]\n"
"\n"
"        self.forward()\n"
"        for sub, effect, dir in zip(subs, effects, dirs):\n"
"            self.show(sub, effect)\n"
"            self.prepare(\n"
"                effect.anim\n"
"                    .points.scale(0.5).to_border(dir, buff=0)\n"
"                    .r.transform.set(scale=0.5)\n"
"            )\n"
"\n"
"        self.forward_to(subs[0].duration)"
msgstr ""
"from janim.imports import *\n"
"\n"
"class _ThreeDShapesExampleSub(Timeline):\n"
"    def __init__(self, shape_type: str, background_color: JAnimColor):\n"
"        super().__init__()\n"
"        self.shape_type = shape_type\n"
"        self.background_color = background_color\n"
"\n"
"    def construct(self):\n"
"        if self.shape_type == 'smooth':\n"
"            axes = ThreeDAxes((-8, 8), (-8, 8), (-8, 8)).apply_depth_test()\n"
"            self.prepare(FadeIn(axes, at=1))\n"
"\n"
"        background = FrameRect(fill_alpha=1, fill_color=self.background_color, stroke_alpha=0, depth=100)\n"
"        background.fix_in_frame()\n"
"        self.prepare(FadeIn(background, at=1.5, duration=3))\n"
"\n"
"        for shape in [Torus(2, 1), Cylinder(2, 4), Cone(2, 4)]:\n"
"            item = shape.into(self.shape_type).show()\n"
"            self.play(self.RotatingCamera(), duration=4)\n"
"            item.hide()\n"
"        \n"
"    def RotatingCamera(self):\n"
"        return AnimGroup(\n"
"            DataUpdater(\n"
"                self.camera,\n"
"                lambda data, p: data.points.rotate(TAU * p.alpha, axis=RIGHT),\n"
"                rate_func=linear\n"
"            ),\n"
"            DataUpdater(\n"
"                self.camera,\n"
"                lambda data, p: data.points.rotate(TAU * p.alpha, axis=OUT),\n"
"                rate_func=linear\n"
"            ),\n"
"        )\n"
"\n"
"class ThreeDShapesExample(Timeline):\n"
"    def construct(self):\n"
"        subs = [\n"
"            _ThreeDShapesExampleSub(type, color).build().to_item()\n"
"            for type, color in zip(\n"
"                ['checker', 'wire', 'smooth', 'dots'],\n"
"                ['#000022', '#000033', '#000033', '#000022']\n"
"            )\n"
"        ]\n"
"        subs[0].show()\n"
"\n"
"        effects = [\n"
"            RectClip(sub, anchor=ORIGIN)\n"
"            for sub in subs\n"
"        ]\n"
"        effects[0].show().depth.set(-1)\n"
"        \n"
"        dirs = [UL, UR, DL, DR]\n"
"\n"
"        self.forward()\n"
"        for sub, effect, dir in zip(subs, effects, dirs):\n"
"            self.show(sub, effect)\n"
"            self.prepare(\n"
"                effect.anim\n"
"                    .points.scale(0.5).to_border(dir, buff=0)\n"
"                    .r.transform.set(scale=0.5)\n"
"            )\n"
"\n"
"        self.forward_to(subs[0].duration)"

